We have presented two talks [1, 2] at the IEEE AP-S Symposium on Antennas and Propagation and USNC-URSI Radio Science Meeting (IEEE-APS/URSI), Boston, MA, USA, July 8-13, 2018.
Moccia, M., Castaldi, G., Alù, A., &amp; Galdi, V. (2018). Spectral singularities in cylindrical non-Hermitian structures. In USNC-URSI Radio Science Meeting. Boston, MA, USA, July 8-13, 2018.
